description.en: Exodia (エクゾディア) – Trade, earn, stake, borrow, leverage on Exodia’s Spot Trading Decentralised Exchange (ExoDEX). An anime-themed DEX that is cooler and first of its kind. Exodia welcomes you to his “Forbidden” Dex – ExoDex, with trading mechanisms that allow limit orders and stop orders turning the impossible to possible. Exodia allows users to obtain the “Win Condition” in DeFi – by using ExoDex, it allows users to get into any token project with insane speed and precision through smart auto slippage and gwei settings.
